short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds some useful features to the chisv tool

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extensions shows the start and end time of the tasks table in your local timezone.

This extension is in no direct relation to CHI or ACM but a private project to enhance user experience of the tool used by student volunteers.
